# Route File Structure

This project uses `remix-flat-routes` for file-based routing.

## Nested route segments

Use **directory nesting** (not dot notation) for multi-segment route paths:

```
# ✅ GOOD — directory nesting
repos/$repoId/cards/$cardId/_route.tsx

# ❌ BAD — dot notation for segments
repos/$repoId/cards.$cardId/_route.tsx
```

Both produce the same URL (`/repos/:repoId/cards/:cardId`), but directory nesting is the project convention.
